  <div class="NewsItem"><a name="5011367122903323887"></a>
         
    <h2 class="post-title">
	 
	 Boston Independence Exchange
	 
    </h2>
    

	         <div class="post-body">
	<div>
      <div style="clear:both;"></div>The Fried Bananas played at the <a href="http://www.youwanttodance.com/newlook/bluescafe.html">Blues Cafe</a> dance during<br />   the <a href="http://freedomofdance.com/">Boston Independance Exchange</a>.  We had a great time and<br />   many of the approximately 300 people there seemed to love dancing to our music so we look forward to<br />   booking some more gigs in the future.<br />  <br /><br /><object width="425" height="355"><param name="movie" value="http://www.youtube.com/v/fON73Ji3s9s&rel=1"></param><param name="wmode" value="transparent"></param><embed src="http://www.youtube.com/v/fON73Ji3s9s&rel=1" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" wmode="transparent" width="425" height="355"></embed></object><br /><br />   <object height="350" width="425"><param name="movie" value="http://www.youtube.com/v/FvgNdrLtNH4"><param name="wmode" value="transparent"><embed src="http://www.youtube.com/v/FvgNdrLtNH4" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" wmode="transparent" height="350" width="425"></embed></object><br />   For more video and audio go to the <a href="http://www.blogger.com/Media.aspx">Media</a> page.<div style="clear:both; padding-bottom:0.25em"></div>
    </div>
    </div>
      
  </div>
  <!-- End .post -->
  
 



  
     
