    <h2 class="post-title">
	 
	 July 20th, 2007 Blues Cafe
	 
    </h2>
    

	         <div class="post-body">
	<div>
      <div style="clear:both;"></div>The Fried Bananas had fun playing again at the <a href="http://www.medfordswings.com">blues cafe</a> dance at <a href="http://springstep.org/">springstep</a> in Medford.<br /><br /><object width="425" height="350"><param name="movie" value="http://www.youtube.com/v/BTVHCupfAro"></param><param name="wmode" value="transparent"></param><embed src="http://www.youtube.com/v/BTVHCupfAro" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" wmode="transparent" width="425" height="350"></embed></object><br /><br />For more video and audio from the gig, go to the <a href="http://www.thefriedbananas.com/Media.aspx">Media</a> page.<div style="clear:both; padding-bottom:0.25em"></div>
    </div>
    </div>
      
