    <h2 class="post-title">
	 
	 First Blues Cafe Gig
	 
    </h2>
    

	         <div class="post-body">
	<div>
      <div style="clear:both;"></div>The Fried Bananas were supposed to play at the Blues Cafe dance on Friday, March 16th. <br />    Unfortunately we got snowed out but Mike Hibarger held a late night party instead.<br />    Video and audio from this party can be found in the <a href="Media.aspx">Media</a><br />    page.<div style="clear:both; padding-bottom:0.25em"></div>
    </div>
    </div>
      
  </div>
  <!-- End .post -->
  
 



  
     
